What is Your Freedom?

YF is a tunneling solution that lets you get fully connected to the Internet even though someone would rather not want you to be connected, and it lets you access services and web sites that are otherwise unaccessible to you. If your Internet access is censored or otherwise restricted, YF will open your door to the world. YF also encrypts your Internet connection and protects you when using open hotspots.

What do I need?

Initially only this app. If you need more bandwidth and usage time than our "FreeFreedom" offer provides, you'll need to set up an account on www.your-freedom.net and use it in the app configuration.

Is it free? What does it cost?

A rudimentary (low bandwidth, limited usage time) access for "unregistered" users is for free. If that's enough for you, you are welcome to keep it this way. Account upgrades may be purchased on our web site and in the in-app store. You'll need to create and use a personal account first. 

Where can I find more information?

On our web site, of course. Click the Settings button, then choose Help.
